children.subject:
I know that you can book appointments with UPE for mock interviews, resume critiques and peer advising and they go over tips and advice that were really helpful when I was interviewing.
https://upe.berkeley.edu/schedule/

history.content:
Hey everyone! I'm an EECS student interning at a tech company, and was wondering whether students would be interested in a decal that helps you prepare for SWE interviews. As someone who has gone through the entire process, I would have really appreciated some guidance when I was first starting out. With the epidemic also negatively affecting the job market, I think a little help in the recruiting department could go a long way this upcoming fall while interviewing for tech internships and jobs. 

Anyhoo, that's enough rambling from me. Please indicate your interest. Also, if anyone is interested in being an instructor, please reach out to techdecal@protonmail.com
history.subject: Would you be interested in a decal that helps you ace tech interviews?
